CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 6, 1965, pg. 15 reads: "Father, Son Banquet - The vestry of the Bethesda United Presbyterian Church, Homewood, was the scene of the annual Father and Son Banquet, sponsored by the Men's League of the church. Guests shown here at the speakers' table are (left to right) Dr. Robert Bolden, Dr. Walter R. Young of Pittsburgh Theological Seminary, speaker; the Rev. Leroy Patrick, host pastor, and George Bullock (standing), president of the Men's League, who is greeting a father-son team, Wilbert Douglas Jr. and son, Wilbert III. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Dr. Robert Bolden, Dr. Walter R. Young, Rev. Leroy Patrick, and George Bullock handing object to Wilbert Douglas Jr. and son, Wilbert Douglas, III, gathered at banquet table for father and son banquet in Bethesda United Presbyterian Church, Homewood
